AB  - Under the influence of intelligent technology, unmanned equipment is gradually popularized and applied in combat, and its effectiveness has been tested and verified. Driven by intelligent unmanned equipment, a big difference is bound to be made in the field of maritime operation, and becoming the new force of maritime rights safeguard operation. This paper analyzes the wining mechanism and internal principles of maritime rights safeguard operations under the influence of intelligent technology, probe into the potential intelligent modes of maritime rights safeguard operations, discuss the advantage and disadvantages and the internal relations of these intelligent operation modes, and puts forward some key technologies, analyze the characters of the technology, which will be of some value to defend the maritime rights and related technology development.
