AB  - The microgrid will become the main power supply method for the community in the future. The rapid development of the cyber-physical system makes the data of the microgrid real-time and transparent, which is helpful for the mutual adjustment between the supply and demand sides. Based on the social cyber-physical system, this paper sets up the CPSS system as a three-layer architecture including the social layer, the information layer and the physical layer, combines the "cloud-pipe-side-end" with the CPSS architecture, and sets the cloud control center and edge server in the information layer. The physical layer is combined with terminal devices to build a CPSS architecture system based on cloud-edge collaborative control. Through the cloud center, the edge servers are controlled cooperatively, and the interactive energy management process of the CPSS system is simulated by combining the "guidance information" and the parallel control system. A microgrid energy management process that combines cloud-edge collaborative control and guidance information is proposed, and an example analysis is carried out. win-win cooperation.
