AB  - This paper presents a method for automated spacecraft docking based on fuzzy logic. Simulation was conducted in the MATLAB tool under a realistic scenario using an Extended Kalman Filter (EKF) for state estimation. The results showed that this method is preferable to Nonlinear MPC in missions requiring lower fuel consumption and short trajectory calculation time. However, the fuzzy controller is characterized by lower accuracy and stability compared to classical control methods. Plots provided can serve as a basis for selecting an appropriate approach based on a comparison of quantitative indicators.
